<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪今天过得并不好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>平时她很喜欢体育课。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，今天她连足球都不想玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>平时她喜欢老师大声读书给他们听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，今天她只希望老师快点读完。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，我们今天要做巧克力饼干！” 尼娜大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪笑了。“我喜欢饼干。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许巧克力饼干可以让她糟糕的一天变成开心的一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也喜欢。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“热乎乎的手工饼干很好吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>围上围裙开始准备吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食材已经放在了桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第一步：把一杯红糖和半杯白糖混合起来。” 贾森念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第二步：加入切好的黄油，搅拌。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把糖和黄油搅拌起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第三步：加两个鸡蛋。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打了鸡蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“第四步：加一茶匙的香草香精。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“搅拌、搅拌、搅拌！” 尼娜提醒伊坦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，在另一个碗里混合干食材。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后我们要一点一点地把干食材加进湿食材里。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“二又四分之一杯面粉。” 波比念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一茶匙小苏打。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一茶匙盐。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有巧克力碎！” 莉琪去拿巧克力碎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她感到头晕。她坐下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>发现自己的头有点疼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，我头疼。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了。” 雪莉老师很担心，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“尼娜，铺一些垫子让莉琪躺下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男生们，把干食材混合进去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜去柜子里拿出几块垫子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男生们准备好了食材。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把饼干面团放到烤盘上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哦！有人预热烤箱了吗？” 雪莉老师突然问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我预热了。” 贾森咧嘴笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 雪莉老师松了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望饼干烤好时，莉琪也会好起来。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她还好吗？” 雪莉老师小声问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她躺下来了。应该已经睡着了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“用190度烤十分钟。” 波比念道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对吗，雪莉老师？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！190度，十分钟。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她叹了口气。“我们开始清理吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好香啊。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以吃一个吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先等一下。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先把饼干放凉。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，莉琪可能想吃饼干。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。你去叫醒她问问吧。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们一起去！把饼干带给她。” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪，你感觉好一点了吗？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪坐起来，打了个哈欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我可能只是需要休息一下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们带了饼干给你。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢！对不起，我没怎么帮忙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪咬了一口饼干，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯！烤得真棒！” 她笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>糟糕的一天终于结束了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>